      "actionDate": "2025-03-21",
      "actionDesc": "Introduced in House",
      "text": "<p><strong>Federal Law Enforcement Officer Service Weapon Purchase Act</strong></p> <p>This bill directs the General Services Administration to establish a program under which a federal law enforcement officer may purchase a retired firearm from the agency that issued the firearm to the officer.</p>",
